<div class="register-01">
    <div class="box">
        <h3>进入观致5 SUV“暖心计划”</h3>
        <div class="input-box">
            <input class="input-01" name="" type="text" placeholder="手机号码" />
            <input class="input-01" name="openid" id="openid" type="hidden" value="<?php echo empty($openid) ? '' : $openid;?>" />
            <span class="close"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="p-01" id="err_tip" style="display:none">
            您是不是输错号码了呢？如果号码正确，则可能订单扔在上传途中，请3-5个工作日后查询。或联系观致客户关怀热线400-920-8088观致5
